'''北卡罗来纳农工州立大学'''（North Carolina Agricultural and Technical State University，亦稱North Carolina A&T State University、North Carolina A&T、N.C. A&T或A&T），是一所位於美國[[北卡罗來納州|北卡罗來納州]][[格林斯伯勒_(北卡罗来纳州)|格林斯伯勒]]的[[公立大學|公立]][[研究型大學|研究型大學]]、[[傳統黑人大學|傳統黑人大學]]，此外在州內還有三個分校區。該大學創建於1891年，為[[北卡罗來納大學|北卡罗來納大學]]的組成機構，也是美國最古老的公立大學之一。<ref name="UNC History">{{cite web|title=220 Years of History|url=http://www.northcarolina.edu/?q=about-our-system/220-years-history|work=University of North Carolina-General Administration|accessdate=26 April 2014|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223163439/https://www.northcarolina.edu/?q=about-our-system%2F220-years-history|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此外它還是美國學生人數最多的傳統黑人大學<ref name="Newsome 2014">{{cite news|last1=Newsome|first1=John|title=N.C. A&T is the nation's largest HBCU|url=http://www.journalnow.com/news/local/n-c-a-t-is-the-nation-s-largest-hbcu/article_eacb3c33-f64f-5f53-8bcf-935beb46a636.html|accessdate=14 October 2014|work=Winston-Salem Journal|date=30 September 2014|archive-date=2017-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817080221/http://www.journalnow.com/news/local/n-c-a-t-is-the-nation-s-largest-hbcu/article_eacb3c33-f64f-5f53-8bcf-935beb46a636.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在全美公立傳統黑人大學中排名第一。<ref name=COE>{{cite web|title=College of Engineering - Points of Pride|url=http://www.ncat.edu/academics/schools-colleges1/coe/About%20the%20College%20/coe-docs-images/coe-documents/COEPointsofPride2.pdf|work=ncat.edu|publisher=N.C. A&T - College of Engineering|accessdate=6 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408222739/http://www.ncat.edu/academics/schools-colleges1/coe/About%20the%20College%20/coe-docs-images/coe-documents/COEPointsofPride2.pdf|archivedate=2014年4月8日}}</ref>

